    "In addition, we focus more on the neural networks due to their complexity.",
    "ML algorithms are often split into three main categories: supervised learning models, unsupervised learning models, and reinforcement learning (RL) models.",
    "Supervised learning is when we have a labeled dataset.",
    "It can be used for classification, where we predict a discrete value, e.g., gender, or regression, where we predict a continuous value, e.g., stock prices.",
    "Unsupervised Learning is when we have an unlabeled dataset."
